{"type": "article", "id": 12687, "title": "世界上最轻的滑板", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-28T07:28:23Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 46, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122502n04uqHIVdZmGjQAX.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t“Stary” 据说是“世界上最轻的滑板”，它采用的是电动机发动，但电动机被放在了滑轮里面，因此不占据滑板的体积，而加上电池，滑板的也重量也只有 8.6 磅。但强大的动力让它的巡航速度可以达到每小时 8.6 英里，每充电一次，可以跑 16 公里，启动和刹车都非常灵活迅速。目前产品正在 Kickstarter 上众筹，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/staryboards/stary-worlds-best-electric-skateboard-get-yours-fo\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看详细信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261404141QAlxGsgmVHLINfj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59793814\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140415fX9pAwJv3ZYGtIiU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.42857143\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140415gJLlQ9w7htcXGFWY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.58823529\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140418p5FzIXPuWhrfNMKC.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"gif\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140422NSpRw0mAMi2lTdZV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.58823529\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140422c6v4dkSpH51u39qz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.58823529\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}